title: Dewit Junior Shovel T-Handle
description: More than a tool, it's an heirloom, The "Junior" Shovel from DeWit is the perfect size for small hands, making it easy and fun to share gardening basics with children. Also a great option for Seniors or gardeners who prefer a lighter tool. Features the T-handle for ease of use. Due to the quality and sharpness of this tool, recommended for ages 8 and up.Constructed of tempered boron steel with ash hardwood handle. This tool is guaranteed a lifetime
